convertir ou à maintenir dans la religion ainsi que les enjeux identitaires qui s’y rattachent. Le lecteur pourra se familiariser avec les expériences contemporaines de plusieurs pays qui intègrent l’enseignement des religions à l’école.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aCatecheticsxCatholic ChurchxHistoryvCongresses. 0aReligionxStudy and teachingvCongresses. 0aReligious educationvCongresses. 7aRELIGION / Education.2bisacsh1 aBonafoux, Corinne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrodeur, Raymond, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaulier, Brigitte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaulier, Brigitte, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCourtois, Luc, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDelpal, Bernard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDurand, Jean-Dominique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEstivalèzes, Mireille, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFavier, Anthony, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFino, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGiorda, Mariachiara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLacroix, Roland, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLalouette, Jacqueline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMartin, Philippe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMellink, Bram, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMolinario, Joël, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMolinario, Joël, eeditor.4